apa sahaja demi anaknya.

53
00:03:46,654 --> 00:03:48,359
Saya batalkan kontrak?

54
00:03:48,754 --> 00:03:50,154
Awak tak tahu?

55
00:03:50,348 --> 00:03:52,447
Tiba-tiba Na Ae Gyo
beritahu saya malam tadi…

56
00:03:52,741 --> 00:03:55,266
