84
00:05:36,492 --> 00:05:37,892
Siapa?

85
00:05:38,975 --> 00:05:40,375
Na Ae Gyo.

86
00:05:40,780 --> 00:05:42,180
Na Ae Gyo...

87
00:05:42,919 --> 00:05:44,452
Ibu kandung Seok Kyung?

88
