Daerah Cheonsoo.

92
00:05:53,902 --> 00:05:56,703
Dia lari dengan duit Dan Tae?

93
00:05:56,907 --> 00:05:58,307
Lebih kurang begitu.

94
00:05:58,834 --> 00:06:00,234
Kenapa awak mahu...

95
00:06:01,106 --> 00:06:02,736
bunuh dia?

96
00:06:03,222 --> 00:06:05,810
Awak suruh saya tolong
awak bunuh seseorang?

97
00:06:06,442 --> 00:06:07,944
Ini bukan kali pertama awak.

98
00:06:09,333 --> 00:06:12,004
Awak tolong Joo Dan Tae
bunuh Su Ryeon,

99
00:06:12,755 --> 00:06:14,155
