103
00:06:27,117 --> 00:06:28,777
Awak tak perlu buat
kalau awak tak mahu.

104
00:06:29,630 --> 00:06:31,550
Kalau awak mahu hidup sengsara
dalam genggamannya…

105
00:06:31,842 --> 00:06:33,442
