146
00:13:10,477 --> 00:13:11,877
Saya tidak apa-apa.

147
00:13:11,902 --> 00:13:13,302
Syukurlah.

148
00:13:14,612 --> 00:13:16,278
Iring dia dengan selamat.

149
00:13:16,683 --> 00:13:18,083
Ini.

150
00:13:18,382 --> 00:13:20,482
Dan Tae beri cincin ini
kepada Ae Gyo.

151
00:13:20,988 --> 00:13:22,521
