kematian Na Ae Gyo)

155
00:15:26,405 --> 00:15:28,975
Tolong uruskan yang lain-lain.

156
00:15:29,000 --> 00:15:30,718
Jaga diri, Logan.

157
00:16:42,012 --> 00:16:43,612
Di mana telefon Dan Tae?

158
00:16:53,427 --> 00:16:55,898
Datang ke tempat simpanan
dengan yang lain-lain sekarang.

159
00:16:57,781 --> 00:16:59,481
