160
00:17:08,009 --> 00:17:09,409
Joo Dan Tae,

161
00:17:09,802 --> 00:17:11,402
inilah pengakhiran awak.

162
00:17:14,261 --> 00:17:16,481
Jangan ke mana-mana dan awasi dia.

163
00:17:24,707 --> 00:17:26,136
