mempercayai saya.

186
00:19:24,185 --> 00:19:25,585
Cik Shim?

187
00:19:27,501 --> 00:19:29,419
Di mana saya?

188
00:19:29,980 --> 00:19:31,718
Saya mahu minta awak...

189
00:19:33,303 --> 00:19:35,133
buat sesuatu yang sukar.

190
00:19:36,952 --> 00:19:38,949
