224
00:24:08,610 --> 00:24:10,027
Apa yang berlaku semalam?

225
00:24:10,212 --> 00:24:12,729
Awak tak sedarkan diri
kerana minum terlalu gopoh.

226
00:24:13,209 --> 00:24:14,736
